lity to sing at precisely the right wavelength to make its foes most drowsy."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"When this POK\u00e9MON sings, it never pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, JIGGLYPUFF cannot breathe, endangering its life."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Nothing can avoid falling asleep hearing a JIGGLYPUFF\u2019s song. The sound waves of its singing voice match the brain waves of someone in a deep sleep."},{"version":"firered","text":"It captivates foes with its huge, round eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing a soothing melody."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"When its huge eyes waver, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep."},{"version":"diamond","text":"When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy."},{"version":"pearl","text":"When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy."},{"version":"platinum","text":"When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If it inflates to sing a lullaby, it can perform longer and cause sure drowsiness in its audience."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Looking into its cute, round eyes causes it to sing a relaxing melody, inducing its enemies to sleep."},{"version":"black","text":"When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy."},{"version":"white","text":"When it wavers its big, round eyes, it begins singing a lullaby that makes everyone drowsy."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Looking into its cute, round eyes makes it start singing a song so pleasant listeners can\u2019t help but fall asleep."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Looking into its cute, round eyes makes it start singing a song so pleasant listeners can\u2019t help but fall asleep."},{"version":"x","text":"It captivates foes with its huge, round eyes, then lulls them to sleep by singing a soothing melody."},{"version":"y","text":"If it inflates to sing a lullaby, it can perform longer and cause sure drowsiness in its audience."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Jigglypuff\u2019s vocal cords can freely adjust the wavelength of its voice. This Pok\u00e9mon uses this ability to sing at precisely the right wavelength to make its foes most drowsy."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"When this Pok\u00e9mon sings, it never pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, Jigglypuff cannot breathe, endangering its life."},{"version":"sun","text":"It hugely inflates its stomach and sings a mysterious melody. If you hear this melody, you\u2019ll become sleepy right away."},{"version":"moon","text":"Jigglypuff possess a vocal range that exceeds 12 octaves, but each individual\u2019s singing skill depends on its own effort."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Recordings of Jigglypuff\u2019s strange lullabies can be purchased from department stores. These CDs can be found near the bedding area."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"The songs they sing are totally different depending on the region they live in. Some even sound like they\u2019re shouting!"},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Uses its cute round eyes to enrapture its foe. It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls the foe to sleep."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Uses its cute round eyes to enrapture its foe. It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls the foe to sleep."},{"version":"sword","text":"Jigglypuff has top-notch lung capacity, even by comparison to other Pok\u00e9mon. It won\u2019t stop singing its lullabies until its foes fall asleep."},{"version":"shield","text":"By freely changing the wavelength of its voice, Jigglypuff sings a mysterious melody sure to make any listener sleepy."}],"evo":{"name":"igglybuff","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":nu